{"tid":1113930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭向中央交禁民族黨報告：維護國家安全是香港特區應有之責","createTime":"2019-04-18T08:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T13:26:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8d2ea1f21ebbe41ea2dbd4c181321dc184e1f4","tid":1113930,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190418/large/1555574391_93ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190418%2Flarge%2F1555574391_93ce.png&h=dbb135d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥公佈，已就港府依法禁止「香港民族黨」運作等有關情況向中央人民政府提交報告，報告中重申警方助理社團事務主任的建議及保安局採取的行動，指民族黨一直採取實質行動以實現其綱領，又指民族黨曾多次提到不排除使用任何方法實現其主張。報告最後亦提到維護國家安全是香港特區應有之責，「港獨」不符合香港特區在《基本法》下的憲制及法律地位，亦與國家對香港既定的基本方針政策相抵觸。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥於4月16日向中央政府提交香港依法禁止「香港民族黨」運作及有關情況的報告，內容包括事件背景和過程摘要等。根據律政司的意見，為避免影響日後可能出現的司法程序，今日公佈的有關報告。報告提及香港政府對「港獨」的立場是十分清晰及明確，任何破壞國家安全的行為都不符合國家利益，更會為香港社會帶來動盪，港府會繼續嚴格按照《基本法》和相關法律，在香港禁止包括「港獨」在內的任何危害國家安全的行為和活動，維護國家安全利益。"},{"pid":"c30be3b7a48378948da82faec190f345f798f81e","tid":1113930,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:08:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190418/59503166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F59503166&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=e0e9956c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190418%2F59503166&h=ec3adb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190418/59503166</a>"},{"pid":"0ad401a17997a3ac9efb67e7444962bea2a4bdf8","tid":1113930,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a878e0de51a6a107346dbf9b5e8db090f2fd862","tid":1113930,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"咁大個國家竟然驚1個人的聲明黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}